                <div1>
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a01"/>神龕　　　　　　乙未八月己亥
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a02"/>　癸巳為皇帝陛下。七世父母。<note n="0041001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30421;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0041001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30421;</rdg></app>生父母。一切眾
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a03"/>　生告<note n="0041002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30422;＝訖【中研院】</note><app n="0041002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">訖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30422;</rdg></app>。夫大<note n="0041003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30433;＝聖【中研院】</note><app n="0041003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">聖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30433;</rdg></app>幽<note n="0041004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30424;＝微【中研院】</note><app n="0041004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">微</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30424;</rdg></app>。以<note n="0041005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30308;＝虛【中研院】</note><app n="0041005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30308;</rdg></app>寂為旨。生<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">成</unclear>
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a04"/>　萬物。功不在己。纖萇通<note n="0041006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30424;＝微【中研院】</note><app n="0041006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">微</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30424;</rdg></app>。咸無不周。大<note n="0041007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30433;＝聖【中研院】</note><app n="0041007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">聖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30433;</rdg></app>
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a05"/>　如味。而研之者明。至言若訥。<note n="0041008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30425;＝尋【中研院】</note><app n="0041008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">尋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30425;</rdg></app>之者辨。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a06"/>　當今皇帝御世。万<note n="0041009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30426;＝邦【中研院】</note><app n="0041009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30426;</rdg></app>斯順。善化垂範。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a07"/>　群迷心返。伏聞一念之善。獲無盡
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a08"/>　之功。一米投<note n="0041010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30427;＝廚【中研院】</note><app n="0041010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">廚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30427;</rdg></app>。致琩F之果。是以張安
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a09"/>　　世。體識<note n="0041011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30308;＝虛【中研院】</note><app n="0041011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30308;</rdg></app>空。識真正法。減<note n="0041012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30428;＝割【中研院】</note><app n="0041012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">割</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30428;</rdg></app>家珍。張
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a10"/>　安世人身造石像一區。上願帝主康寧。祚延
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a11"/>　無窮。若洛三徒。不逕八難。下願張安世人身家
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a12"/>　眷。合無大小。無病少<note n="0041013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30430;＝痛【中研院】</note><app n="0041013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">痛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30430;</rdg></app>。延年益<note n="0041014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30431;＝壽【中研院】</note><app n="0041014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">壽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30431;</rdg></app>。宅舍全
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a13"/>　<note n="0041015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30432;＝鋼【中研院】</note><app n="0041015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">鋼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30432;</rdg></app>。來財宜寶。用之無盡。所願從心。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a14"/>　祖張豐洛。父周慶。叔父雙慶。兄文虯。兄文清。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a15"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　兄賢黃。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a16"/>　名安世。息還洛。息阿僧。息僧歡。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a17"/>　妻李男異。妾王阿引。息富洛。息雙富。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a18"/>　姪阿洛。姪阿歡。姪阿奴。姪天還。姪似仁。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0041a19"/>　姪德仁。姪□歡。
                </div1>
